[~viglesias]/[~tony]:

Issue is not fixed.  Using custom and AWS example for nested cloudformation template, stack failed to create with the following error:
{code}
<Stack Name> must be alphanumeric and start with a letter
{code}
Same template worked on AWS.  In order to test this, I needed to use the AWS CLI tools (1.6.10) due to the following euca2ools issues:
* TOOLS-535
* TOOLS-536

